eight=342 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MILITARY BASE IN THE DESERT</h2><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION</h2><br>All weapons from real-world prototypes. Our talented team created them to give a fascinating gameplay feeling. We are for fair and balanced matches without any weapon improvement systems.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/ff0d05c2541f8b731b3a5bcdf3eadc55.poster.avif?t=1716010361\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/ff0d05c2541f8b731b3a5bcdf3eadc55.webm?t=1716010361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/ff0d05c2541f8b731b3a5bcdf3eadc55.mp4?t=1716010361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Weather </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/e86c203d5d2bad2eb1a5f12e6797c5bc.poster.avif?t=1716010361\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/e86c203d5d2bad2eb1a5f12e6797c5bc.webm?t=1716010361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/e86c203d5d2bad2eb1a5f12e6797c5bc.mp4?t=1716010361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extensive maps with underground structures and open spaces.</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769930/extras/4a90666f13d9963fd37fe333e4f7da24.avif?t=1716010361\" width=574 height=342 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared